'''High Marshal''' was a [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] military rank used during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] by the [[Iron Knight]]s. High Marshals were appointed by the [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellor]]. [[Ilum (Jedi)|Ilum]] and [[Dragite (Jedi)|Dragite]] were High Marshals when they reemerged years before the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. High Marshal is also the highest rank in the mercenary group, [[Ailon Nova Guard/Legends|Ailon Nova Guard]].

